arabia said henry harris a 51yearold teacher but its our 
duty to go 
the reasons the men did join the guard are varied money 
education security friendship some joined because they served in 
the regular military others because they hadnt 
i wanted to try something different said sgt earnest 
deloach i guess i got different 
the national guard offers members a variety of advantages the 
first is money for serving one weekend a month and two weeks each 
summer a guardsman can get a minimum of 4000 to 8000 a year 
depending on rank and years of service 
the salaries and other guard spending can add up for a 
community in allendale county the guard estimates it has a 1 
million impact on the economy 
a second reason to join is security if you complete 20 years of 
service you get a pension and guaranteed health care for you and 
your spouse more than half the 265th has 16 or more years of 
service already 
the guard also offers education you can attend special schools 
that teach you a trade there also are programs to help pay college 
expenses 
spc bobby youmans another prison guard had planned to start 
college under the program his callup has put those plans off 
but youmans spoke of another reason he joined the guard 11 years 
ago 
it gives you a chance to meet with other people he said 
you get to move in other circles instead of going with the same 
crowd every weekend you can hang out with the people you meet 
through your unit 
youmans 29 explained all this to young a newcomer who has 
been in the unit three years 
young is whippetthin and usually quiet until he steps out on 
the basketball court then he is a oneman cheering section 
talking incessantly yelling for the ball and giggling hoarsely 
when he runs down the court his face is in near joy 
young and youmans work together on the middle shift in the 
maximum security lockup at the allendale correctional institution 
riding back from the gym they wondered if the guys back at the 
prison miss them youmans thought they might 
young didnt seem to care 
thats one job i aint in no hurry to get back to he said 
