obsession with the asian games has done little to win public 
support among residents who were asked to make contributions to 
the 53 million fund needed to stage the games 
we have a bad government said one chinese salesman were 
poor but they took even more money away from us to pay for the 
asian games it doesnt do us any good 
the government has tightened security in the city to gird 
against possible terrorist attacks or protests by students and 
workers seeking to take advantage of the large foreign presence 
during the asian games 
