owereeowes are not cookies hawn 
in the city that natives call bawlmer owereeowes are orioles 
baltimore has a curious mix of southern northern pennsylvania 
dutch appalachian and various immigrant speech patterns and 
bawlmerese is most apparent in its stressed o sound heard in 
words such as oweshun and awl thats ocean and oil 
its not fully northern and not fully southern said allan 
metcalfe executive secretary of the american dialect society 
for example baltimore is on the border of where cot and 
caught are said the same he said 
