of personal power karbainov told a news conference for soviet 
and foreign reporters in the lubyanka the drab downtown 
headquarters of the security service 
the soviet foreign and domestic intelligence operations are 
combined in one service the kgb unlike the united states where 
the functions are divided between the central intelligence agency 
and the federal bureau of investigation 
during the news conference karbainov disclosed little new about 
the internal workings of the kgb arguing it was necessary to 
preserve secrecy about operations budget and the number of 
employees 
everything relating to the aims directions and results of kgb 
work should be open to the public while methods forms and 
techniques used to perform specific operations and security agents 
should remain hidden from public view for the timebeing he said 
