504 colleges and universities surveyed still did not require 
foreignlanguage and literature courses 
but business demands are perhaps the biggest key 
people have got to be shown that theres a place to use it 
said lambert of the national foreign language center if we can 
establish that theres more need for foreign languages in the 
business world and elsewhere then well be seeing an upward trend 
for a long time 
