but let the buyer beware the amount of training received by 
guaranteed graduates may vary some schools simply warranty all 
their graduates in others the warranty program is designed mainly 
for students who want jobs straight out of high school 
at prince georges county school district in maryland students 
who want to be under warranty take a semester class focusing on job 
skills the class has been developed with input from area business 
and industry leaders 
