tumbling by rumors that iraqi president saddam hussein had lost 
power that rumor had its own brief effects on the us markets 
first i believe it was that there had been a coup and then 
someone said he had been killed and thats how the rumor 
started said ed kevelson a trader with dean witter reynolds 
inc it affected asia and it somewhat affected our opening here 
but by the time it got here it had been discounted 
